snippet.title: REDDER official trailer
snippet.description:
REDDER is a game about being lost in space.

First released as a web game in 2010, an updated desktop version can be downloaded at https://w.itch.io/redder

The saxophone cover of the REDDER theme that plays in this video is by subversiveasset. Hear more at https://www.youtube.com/user/subversiveasset
